description: FireHouse BBQ is Real Deal BBQ at it's best... We started out in 1996 as a competition BBQ team from Orlando.  FireHouse has been featured on Foodnetwork and Winner on TLC's All-Start BBQ Pitmasters as the best Brisket in the country. We are now a BBQ catering company/ Mobile food truck in Central Florida.  We bring the party to the party.  Let us show you what Real BBQ tastes like.  FireHouse BBQ started a new moblie Food Truck with a full commercial kitchen and smokers built in.
name: FireHouse BBQ
